<HEADLINE> Taiwan is an Integral Part of China, Vietnam Reiterates </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HANOI, December 1 (Xinhua) -- "Vietnam recognizes the
government of the People's Republic of China as the only legal
government representing China as a whole," Vietnam News Agency
reported Tuesday, quoting a Foreign Ministry spokesperson.
</P>
<P>
