by the Zimbabwean high court on all the sodomy, attempted sodomy
and indecent assault charges brought against him.
</P>
<P>
"The Zimbabwean police and Interpol are working together to
bring Banana back to the country as soon as possible and they
will not give him the chance to fly to south America as rumored,"
said the official.
</P>
<P>
The former president, who was head of state since independence
in 1980 up to 1987, skipped bail.
</P>
<P>
On allegations that the state let Banana run away, the
official said it was false, adding that if he was brought back,
he would be sentenced just like any other offender.
</P>
<P>
